.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
Nationality: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
Music-Genre: gospel, classical, ambient, rock, disco
House: craftsman, palace, futuristic, tower, gothic-revival
Pet: cat, bird, dog, fish, horse
1. Nationality:british == Color:red
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:dog
3. Nationality:danish == Music-Genre:rock
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Music-Genre:classical
6. House:futuristic == Pet:bird
7. Color:yellow == House:palace
8. Music-Genre:ambient is in the middle
9. Nationality:norwegian is on the far left
10. House:gothic-revival is on the left or right of Pet:cat
11. Pet:horses is on the left or right of House:palace
12. House:craftsman == Music-Genre:gospel
13. Nationality:german == House:tower
14. Nationality:norwegian is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. House:gothic-revival is on the left or right of Music-Genre:disco

